        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 24pt;">Thank you for your time.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 14pt;">
            <p>Brandon Matias | bmatias98@outlook.com</p>
            <p>linkedin.com/in/brandonmatias</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
"""

